column2: "Oh, it's you. Coincidence running into you here."
"This planet seems off in a lot of ways. I get bad feelings every time I'm here."
"Not only Darkers, but also ARKS as well. There seem to be a bunch of other things mixed in as well."
"There seem to be a lot of small native creatures around here as well."
"It seemed like I was about to get caught up in something, so I ran away here."
"It wasn't a Darker. I didn't see exactly what it was, but I wonder what it could have been."
